data.description: Elegant single-family home with breathtaking mountain and city light views. Nestled in a serene setting with no neighbors across, this residence offers tranquility and privacy. The home is meticulously crafted with a well-thought-out layout, creating a seamless flow between rooms. The interior is tastefully designed, offering both comfort and elegance for a harmonious living experience. The dual sided fireplace divides both the living room and family room giving both spaces a cozy feel. The kitchen and Master bathroom have been tastefully redone with beautiful granite counters. Relax out back in your own private oasis. The backyard is spacious, perfect for outdoor gatherings, with the added convenience of potential RV parking, adding versatility to your lifestyle. This remarkable home truly has it all including an oversized two-car garage, ensuring ample space for your vehicles. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this house your home! *This home borders the city of Rialto and is part of the Rialto Unified School District.*
